data.description: This acreage is the one you have been waiting for! INCREDIBLE views of the Platte River Valley off a quiet cul de sac. Close to Omaha, Lincoln, shopping and Interstate – this 1.5 story features spacious living areas and the perfect layout for entertaining. The grand entry greets guests and leads to a curved staircase. Kitchen features oversized refrigerator, double oven, induction cook top and pantry with 2nd microwave. The main level primary has a soaking tub, double sink, large closet and upgraded shower. Main floor office features a custom, built in murphy bed. Upstairs bedrooms share a unique hang out space with built in homework desks. The finished basement features full kitchen, the perfect set up to watch all the games, and a large storage/storm shelter area. Other features include: geothermal heating system, soft close cabinets throughout and upgraded finishes. Watch gorgeous sunsets from the low maintenance covered deck. House has transferable home warranty good thru 2029.
